channel.title: Error On Downloaded Client! Loggs out every 1 - 5 minutes!
channel.description:
:eek: :eek: :eek: :eek: It has really been aggravating for me, being the owner of a server, when im talking to some players and im logged out... Here is what it often says: Error: T2 - 81,65,81 - 61,2611,3093 - 3,32,127,0,8,21,0,0,29,6,27,-86,8,-88,31,113,20,-107,28,-23,0,17,-9,1,3,11,-69,29,8,1,14,1,0,0,0,0,5,-14,3,55,3,51,3,52,3,53,3,54,3,56,
or: Error: T1 - 56,0 - 44,126
or some variation of that... if you can help me at all PLEASE DO SO!!!
